sub_title: Msc Econometrics (Logistics) - Data scientist and mathematics teacher
summary: I am a driven go-getter, hard-working and analytically strong. From September 2022 onwards, I work as a maths teacher in Veenendaal, the Netherlands, as well as being a data-scientist (fitting to my background in Econometrics and Logistics). I am available as a freelancer via my small business WisWish, for solutions that include knowledge on Econometrics. Please feel free to get in touch.
